TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select fcst_sku_key, fiscal_year, fiscal_period, BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, SUM(forecast_quantity) as forecast_quantity from fcst_sku_sales_forecast_week GROUP BY BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID,fcst_sku_key,fiscal_year, fiscal_period HAVING SUM(forecast_quantity)<>0 order by fcst_sku_key ,BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST.REGULAR_SALES_QTY as REGULAR_SALES_QTY, FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST.FISCAL_YEAR as FISCAL_YEAR, FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST.FISCAL_PERIOD as FISCAL_PERIOD, LTRIM(RTRIM(FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST.SKU_KEY)) as SKU_KEY FROM FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST FCST_MONTHLY_CAPACITY_FORECAST

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ITEM_ID = I_ITEM_ID AND FISCAL_YEAR = I_FISCAL_YEAR AND FISCAL_PERIOD = I_FISCAL_PERIOD AND SKU_KEY = I_SKU_KEY
